script replaces occupancy and beta values with new taken from input file

replace_beta6.pl pdb_file values params 2

parameters:
	beta
		=1 replace beta factors 
		=2 replace occupancy and beta factors

	as_beta - number of column to take beta factor replacment
	as_occup - number of column to take occupancy replacement
	normalized
		=! 1 values not normalized (default) 
		=1 values normalized

